These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, orange, amber, green
House: gothic-revival, art-deco, townhouse, tower
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, poppy, bellflower, azalea
There are 4 different nationalities: british, japanese, colombian, indonesian
 1. the person who growspoppy is not to the right of the person who growssunflower##8
 2. the british is not to the left of the british##8
 3. the indonesian is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who growssunflower is not to the left of the person who growsazalea##8
 5. the british is not to the right of the british##8
 6. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 7. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the right of the person who likes chestnut##5
 8. the tower house is between the japanese and the person who growspoppy##2
 9. the indonesian is the townhouse house##1
10. the indonesian is on the right of the person who likes green##1
11. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
12. the person who likes green is somewhere to the right of the person who likes orange##5
13. the townhouse house is not to the left of the indonesian##8
14. the person who likes orange is the colombian##1
15. the person who likes orange is not the person who growspoppy##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Color         | chestnut     | orange   | green | amber |
| House   | art-deco | tower   | gothic-revival   | townhouse  |
| Flower         | poppy  | bellflower  | azalea  | sunflower |
| Nationality     | british    | colombian | japanese     | indonesian    |

