.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, light-blue, green, lavender
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, january, october
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, motorbike, airplane, taxi
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, singing, camping
 1. the person driving the airplane is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person driving the motorbike##2
 2. the person who likes light-blue is not to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
 3. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
 4. the person who likes lilac is not to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##8
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the person who likes lavender##8
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
11. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
12. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
13. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
14. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
15. the person who likes lilac is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
17. the person who likes lilac is not to the right of the person driving the motorbike##8
18. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
19. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
