 4. the swisher-smoker is between the person watching drama movies and the person watching animation movies##2
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 6. the art-deco house is not to the right of the swisher-smoker##8
 7. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 9. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person watching animation movies is the art-deco house##1
11. the palace house is not to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##8
12. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the palace house##3
13. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
14. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the palace house##3
