 5. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the right of the person who growsrose##8
 6. the person driving the van is not to the right of the person traveling to marseilles##8
 7. the person driving the boat is not to the left of the owner of the frog##8
 8. the person who growsaconite is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 9. the person who growstulip is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
10. the person traveling to colone is not to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##8
11. the person driving the taxi is between the owner of the goat and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
12. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person driving the van##1
13. the person who growsaconite is not to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##8
14. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3

.:: Answer ::.
