16. the vegafina-smoker is not to the right of the person who likes chestnut##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Cigar           | vegafina | bongani       | bolivar      | alhambra  |
| Color   | white    | amber | chestnut   | emerald   |
| Beverage   | fanta   | coffee          | 7up      | mirinda  |
| Pet   | goat   | snake      | pony | chinchilla |

